data.description: Don't miss this great opportunity. Upgraded corner-end unit, the largest floor plan at Regal Palms Resort. Features 2 master suites, one with a balcony.  Turnkey, close to clubhouse. Laminate  floors on 1st floor, elegant European-style tiled bathrooms; upgraded  carpet in 2nd floor bedrooms. Ideal for primary residence or short-term rental. Regal Palms Resort offers luxury living, 15 mins from Disney World. Enjoy a tropical swimming pool, lazy river oasis, heated pools, water slide, Jacuzzis, playground, and more. Fitness center, spa, restaurant, bar, entertainment, and market on-site.
